"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-nothing-special-by-nicole-flattery-c8dd6546"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-815081?width=700&amp;height=403" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit"></span></div></div></div><p>另外还有丹尼尔·霍恩斯比 (Daniel Hornsby) 的《Sucker》和安德鲁·利普斯坦 (Andrew Lipstein) 的《The Vegan》。<em>萨克斯评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/fiction-nothing-special-by-nicole-flattery-c8dd6546?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/gwen-john-review-putting-her-in-the-picture-e8d132a6?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">“格温·约翰”评论：把她放在画面中</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
